{"tid":382895,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"「新機快報」最近發表嘅兩部入門無反 E-M10III & Eos M100","createTime":"2017-09-01T05:13:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T09:39:51.000Z","uid":523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ff22503f6c6c16eec8fffcfadb156521eaf93e47","tid":382895,"uid":523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T05:13:41.000Z","msg":"E-M10III ：<br />\n轉：<a href=\"http://photo.popart.hk/newweb/archives/175577\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphoto.popart.hk%2Fnewweb%2Farchives%2F175577&d=Iyc%2FzmFkNyrh6TxhnKm0375jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=5d2ed51d\" target=\"_blank\">http://photo.popart.hk/newweb/archives/175577</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photo.popart.hk/newweb/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Bildschirmfoto-2017-08-31-um-10.03.45.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphoto.popart.hk%2Fnewweb%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2FBildschirmfoto-2017-08-31-um-10.03.45.png&h=0dcd55ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photo.popart.hk/newweb/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Olympus-OM-E-E-M10-Mark-III-camera-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphoto.popart.hk%2Fnewweb%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2FOlympus-OM-E-E-M10-Mark-III-camera-1.jpg&h=518b5678&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這台新推出的<span style=\"color: red;\">1600萬像素M43無反相機</span>，帶來<span style=\"color: red;\">4K</span>超高清視頻拍攝，ISO範圍100-25,600，最高可達<span style=\"color: red;\">8.6 fps</span>連拍，及皇牌<span style=\"color: red;\">5軸防震</span>。<br />\n<br />\nEos M100 ：<br />\n轉：<a href=\"http://www.dcfever.com/news/readnews.php?id=20141\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dcfever.com%2Fnews%2Freadnews.php%3Fid%3D20141&d=Iyc%2FzmFkNyrh6TxhnKm0375jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=396cac9c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.dcfever.com/news/readnews.php?id=20141</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn01.dcfever.com/articles/news/2017/08/170829_m200_03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn01.dcfever.com%2Farticles%2Fnews%2F2017%2F08%2F170829_m200_03.jpg&h=60f10a5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n機能上 M100 提升就相當明顯，當中焦點之一肯定就是 M100 亦如 M5 / M6 般改用了一片支援 <span style=\"color: red;\">Dual Pixel CMOS AF 技術的 2420 萬像 APS-C CMOS</span>，大大加強了相機的對焦反應。配合新的 DIGIC 7 影像處理器之下，相機追焦連拍方面亦由 M10 的 2.2fps 提高至 <span style=\"color: red;\">4fps</span>，鎖定 AF 之下，相機的連拍更可進一步提高至 <span style=\"color: red;\">6.1fps</span>。<br />\n<br />\n雖然 M100 並未支援 4K 拍片，不過相機攝錄規格上亦有一定進步，由 1080/30p 改為支援更流蜴的 <span style=\"color: red;\">1080/60p</span>，新機並內置有 Wi-Fi 及 Bluetooth，作為一般生活拍攝用機，功能已算是齊全。"},{"pid":"32af66da923dce36f726b54898e030526fd23af0","tid":382895,"uid":69434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T05:18:56.000Z","msg":"olympus完勝"},{"pid":"0f03a45e59c44f4cf61eeb9db332e434eea0f839","tid":382895,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T08:59:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>olympus完勝</blockquote><br />\n2017新機唔支援4k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e50e7cb19ca8f98d731e7c4701874c7199959eb1","tid":382895,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T08:59:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>olympus完勝</blockquote><br />\n2017新機唔支援4k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ni mean canon"},{"pid":"4a0999eec3b64069dc52c0ef6934d0ac1ba2a89d","tid":382895,"uid":60074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T11:06:22.000Z","msg":"放唔放mkii換mkiii好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a384410c823dd24a76486ada7a33d9e42e3443","tid":382895,"uid":52030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T11:24:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>放唔放mkii換mkiii好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇乜意思，一換就升級唔平行換代<br />\n新買可以諗跌兩波再買"},{"pid":"91c6f3e8e05f93912f775b0de6764738b073f